<?php

namespace App\DTO;

use Spatie\LaravelData\Attributes\MapInputName;
use Spatie\LaravelData\Attributes\MapOutputName;
use Spatie\LaravelData\Attributes\Validation\ArrayType;
use Spatie\LaravelData\Attributes\Validation\IntegerType;
use Spatie\LaravelData\Attributes\Validation\Required;
use Spatie\LaravelData\Attributes\Validation\StringType;
use Spatie\LaravelData\Data as SpatieLaravelDataObj;

class TestDTO extends SpatieLaravelDataObj
{
	/**
	 * @param string $string
	 * @param int $int
	 * @param float $float
	 * @param string[]|null $stringArray
	 * @param int[]|null $intArray
	 * @param mixed $emptyArray
	 * @param \App\DTO\NestedArray $nestedArray
	 */
	public function __construct(
		public $string,
		public $int,
		public $float,
		#[MapInputName('string_array'), MapOutputName('string_array'), ArrayType('StringType::class')] public $stringArray,
		#[MapInputName('int_array'), MapOutputName('int_array'), ArrayType('IntegerType::class')] public $intArray,
		#[MapInputName('empty_array'), MapOutputName('empty_array'), Required] public $emptyArray,
		#[MapInputName('nested_array'), MapOutputName('nested_array')] public $nestedArray,
	) {
	}
}
